name: The White Void(DEMO)
description:
This game is just a Demo I made to see if peaple would like the game so if you like the game comment here so that I know

The full game will have much more content as this demo is only 3 Levels

It is a demo but there are some Easter Eggs like the dark man screenshot(You wont find him normally) to find him: get to an amount of Deaths and jump into the biggest hole you see in the game.
